title: BRAND NEW UNIT IN PARAISO BAY!
posting_body: ['BRAND NEW 1 bed/2 bath + Den corner unit in Paraiso Bay with stunning water views from every angle.', 'High end finishes & upgrades.', 'Den has a glass enclosure which easily can be used as a second bedroom/office/study room.', 'Motorized window treatments,fully upgraded lighting,built out closets & movable island.', 'Bosch and Sub-Zero appliances.', 'Luxurious 5 star amenities which include.', "State of the art Gym & Spa,Wine room,Cigar Lounge,Billiard Room,Movie theater,Children's playroom,Business Center,Lounge,100 diameter beach entry pool,Cabanas,Out door grill,2 tennis courts,Bayfront Park with docks and boardwalk.", 'Access to private beach club only for residents.', 'GREAT location minutes to the Beaches, Design District, Wynwood, Downtown and Brickell.', '1 assigned parking space.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
